abstracts.cdata!:
The Project aims to further strengthen
            ADBP as a sound and effective institution focusing
            principally on lending to smaller farmers. It would provide,
            through ADBP, loans to farmers for medium- and long-term
            agricultural investments in farm mechanization, implements
            and equipment, private minor irrigation, on-farm development
            and dairy animals.
